{"tid":1242203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再散播失敗言論","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T02:37:26.000Z","uid":12138,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3b67ff0d6f8bb577d755cc9ac37456b0868e3ad9","tid":1242203,"uid":12138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:26:08.000Z","msg":"唔該各位同路人（我當你地唔係鬼）<br />\n唔好再散播失敗言論<br />\n日日係到講咩市民大眾攰啦/21號宣傳唔夠/林鄭態度軟化<br />\n而家我地4樣訴求<br />\n政府一樣都無回應<br />\n我地行動咁都唔升級？<br />\n如果我地咁樣都接受<br />\n政府以後就唔會再理民意（雖然而家都係）<br />\n更何況我地對得住犧牲左/比人拉左既義士？<br />\n<br />\n話我地21號宣傳唔夠既咪幫手宣傳<br />\nshare比身邊既人<br />\n一傳十十傳百<br />\n我地612都係咁樣做嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n大家真係唔可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e236204d93cdb1d4bea267d423828d3fa8e1e5c3","tid":1242203,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究黑警濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61f57262b77e34fdde75e286f1592989aa045a0","tid":1242203,"uid":232921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"政府最痛之處應該係拉倒國歌法同明日大🐠⋯⋯"},{"pid":"6707768168c10e39e47f048e32cf1afafc707111","tid":1242203,"uid":222659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"只許成功不許失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3de072ebd855856965b246095985dd40af8fc8","tid":1242203,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f61f57262b77e34fdde75e286f1592989aa045a0","tid":1242203,"uid":232921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"政府最痛之處應該係拉倒國歌法同明日大🐠⋯⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n依兩個先係真章"},{"pid":"f417774157dfa9c09c04e1ac96b42016c63a8a2d","tid":1242203,"uid":232921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:33:43.000Z","msg":"各施各法，民間有民間保持一個熱度，議員有議員拉布。"},{"pid":"5089ff347cb23cc85b878ed2753b62ad2c10971a","tid":1242203,"uid":12138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f61f57262b77e34fdde75e286f1592989aa045a0","tid":1242203,"uid":232921,"like":0,"